&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.oliv.ai/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Oliv.AI&lt;/a&gt; is a SalesTech global startup headquartered in San Francisco, debuting the world&#39;s first team of AI Agents for sales. With our recent $5.2M Seed funding,&amp;nbsp;we solve one of the biggest problems for revenue teams: unreliable deal data. Oliv captures Deal Intelligence from every meeting, call, and email—without any rep involvement. The result is a clear, detailed view of every deal, presented in scorecards built on trusted sales methodologies like MEDDICC, BANT, and SPICED.&amp;nbsp;Our AI agents are built for sales teams—sales managers, AEs, and RevOps—handling the work that takes them away from selling. With Oliv AI, sales teams can bring back focus on deals, strategy and conversation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
